Package: InvestigatoR
Type: Package
Title: Machine Learning for Factor Investing with R
Version: 0.2.0
Description: The package provides a front-end to backtesting investment portfolios using various machine learning and weighting algorithms. It is based on various features from the book Machine Learning for Factor Investing  at <https://www.mlfactor.com/> by Guillaume Coqueret.
